title: Spyder Auto Installation: 2002-05 BMW 3-Series 4-Door (E46) LED Tail Lights
description: This video demonstrates how to install a set of Light Bar LED style tail lights on 2002 through 2005 BMW 3-Series 4-door models (E46). This tutorial offers a complete walkthrough of the installation process from start to finish with helpful information throughout to facilitate a successful installation.
